snippet.title: Skyscraper In-Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Hi, Hikers

Skyscraper's in-game trailer has been released.
In the trailer, you can see the Skyscraper in-game play, the world map, and the characters.

And any feedback is welcome, so please leave it in the comments!
Follow our official community and keep up to date with the latest news.

👉 Discord: https://discord.gg/Nh2jG5Zqwc
👉 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Skyscrapers21
👉 Twitter: https://twitter.com/SS_official_A

See you soon, Hikers!
